************
**SHAMITAB**
************
Luc Kuenemann

COMPILING:
**********
To compile:
make
To clean everything:
make clean

RUNNING:
********
To view a tablature:
./shamitab view [path-to-tab.3mt] [bars per line]

To convert a text tablature to 3mt format:
./shamitab convert [path-to-tab.txt] [path-to-converted-tab.3mt]

To display a list of all available commands:
./shamitab help


